The mineralocorticoid effects of high dose hydrocortisone." BMJ 310 (1995): 656-7[5] Powell JR "Steroid and hypokalemic myopathy after corticosteroids for ulcerative colitis. Systemic and tropical application." Am J Gastroenterol 52 (1969): 425-32[6] Thorn GW "Clinical considerations in the use of corticosteroids." N Engl J Med 274 (1966): 775-81[7] Seale JP, Compton MR "Side-effects of corticosteroid agents." Med J Aust 144 (1986): 139-42[8] Chrousos GA, Kattah JC, Beck RW, Cleary PA "Side effects of glucocorticoid treatment. Experience of the Optic Neuritis Treatment Trial." JAMA 269 (1993): 2110-2', 1767365205);
